
// ============================================================
//  AHWA Governance — persistent-stake on-chain governance
//
//  Voters stake AHWA once and gain ongoing voting power = staked balance.
//  Stake stays locked until they unstake (which nullifies any open votes).
//  Vote weight is recorded on-chain in the contract's tally — no event scan
//  is needed to compute the result. The page reads two values per proposal
//  (totalYesWeight, totalNoWeight) directly from contract state.
// ============================================================

